"_Honra and glory the comrade Norah!_

_The first congress yields deep and solemn tribute to comrade Norah, member of the red and proven communist fraction, great and example is the party's life and the revolution, the most high-ender-worse-worse-woe, gonzalo, firm and firm wankeeper and revolution. Always consistent antirevismionist. The biggest heroine in the party._

