# SANDRA LIMA: The wholeness of a proletarian revolutionary

Author: Movimento Feminino Popular

Time: 2023-03-06T16:38:00-03:00

Images: ['[HO6xXOpj9v6O3qu_VNIJhNCCOGjMV9sagwrLMtGrfGu_BYEAZPCFTlCbz-WTNsG2ALriyElOfWCB1A4=w283-h400](https://1.bp.blogspot.com/HO6xXOpj9v6O3qu_VNIJhNCCOGjMV9sagwrLMtGrfGu_BYEAZPCFTlCbz-WTNsG2ALriyElOfWCB1A4=w283-h400)']

Tags: []

<!--METADATA-->

[![](Images/Movimento Feminino Popular/2023-03-06T16-38-00-03-00/HO6xXOpj9v6O3qu_VNIJhNCCOGjMV9sagwrLMtGrfGu_BYEAZPCFTlCbz-WTNsG2ALriyElOfWCB1A4=w283-h400)](https://1.bp.blogspot.com/HO6xXOpj9v6O3qu_VNIJhNCCOGjMV9sagwrLMtGrfGu_BYEAZPCFTlCbz-WTNsG2ALriyElOfWCB1A4=s400)"_ It is not a difficult task for the revolutionary of our time in our country in honor of our dear companion Sandra Lima. Now, past a month of the bump that we have been affected, after the tremors of the floor under our feet, we can speak with the heart in less ENOS SUPPLY calls reason to do so with the reality and concreteness that life consumes us in the face of death.

_No that we surrender in the face of death because it is, at one point, inevitable for each of us, for each living being, for above all, amort is not only death, it is also life. It is also with her that humanity will be produced and continues its saga towards the future. We came from others, who from others have been born from us others and of these others, so many others and assimindinly in a process that encompasses eras, eras, steps, phases, moments, anyway. In the infinity of the universe wouldn't it be a strange selfishness and to oven we live forever in the same way and space? But death reaps many out of its time. But for the true revolutionaries your life is not donated to the cause?

_It of all, because it is necessary to see life or as isolated individuals and nor a jumble of them, to see life as the human collectivity in their hundreds of thousands of years struggling to transform the world, heroic narche of the kingdom of necessity for the need to Kingdom of Freedom.___

_The companion Sandra is among us, her presence is already in our beads, in our consigns, in our songs, in our words and the ladies of our people as inextinguishable and luminous red star!"_

Excerpt from the Revolutionary Front Pronouncement for the Defense of the Rights of the Popovo at the time of the celebration in honor of the companion Sandra Limarealized in 2016 in Belo Horizonte.



For the entire revolutionary movement of our country and internationalist to the companion, it was decidedly, the loss of companion Sandra Lima weighing a mountain. The great shower president Mao Tsetung said Hamoes weighing less than a pity, while others weigh more than the Montetai(A large lot located in northeast of China). A morte dosreacionários, inimigos do povo, pesa menos que uma pena, enquanto a morte dosrevolucionários pesa mais que uma montanha. Ao prestar homenagem a nossagrande, valorosa, querida e imortal companheira de longa marcha revolucionáriaqueremos destacar que este acontecimento se reveste de significado especial,além de conhecer sua trajetória, compreender o significado da sua militânciapara difundir seu exemplo e generalizar sua experiência.

A querida companheira Sandra Lima faleceu no dia 27 de julho de 2016, aos 61anos de idade. A companheira nasceu no dia 6 de março de 1955 em São Domingosdo Prata, interior de Minas Gerais. Ficou órfã de mãe quando completaria 4anos de idade, fato que determinaria sua "vida de cigana", como costumavareferir-se aos anos de sua infância e juventude. Quando sua mãe morreu deixou5 filhos, o mais velho com 7 anos e o caçula com menos de 1 ano de idade. Suaavó materna Jupira se muda então para Barão de Cocais para assumir a criaçãodos netos, aos 54 anos, ela era viúva e havia criado seus 5 filhos sozinha.

Após a morte da mãe, a companheira Sandra passou mais 3 anos em Barão deCocais; depois, fez os 3 primeiros anos de Grupo Escolar em Belo Horizonte;fez o 4º ano de grupo e a 1ª série do Ginásio em São Domingos do Prata; as 2ªe 3ª séries em Itabirito; e a 4ª série novamente em Belo Horizonte. Muitodedicada aos estudos, esteve entre os melhores alunos da turma.

**Uma jovem contestadora e rebelde**

In 1969 Sandra moves with her grandmother to Belo Horizonte. Dona Jupira sets up apension on Avenida Paraná, where she houses two grandchildren and friends of Itabirito that came to study in the capital. In August 1970, when Sandra had 15 years, her grandmother abruptly leaves the house. The immediate cause of the rupture was a letter that Sandra had written to a pension colleague where she criticized her grandmother's authoritarian omodo. Dona Jupira reads the letter and, when late morning arrives from school, they were waiting for two aunts and an older cousin, the family doctor. Upon seeing the letter in her grandmother she was already sure of what she would be at that unexpected meeting. Before receiving the Decriters Saraiva, he cleaned the ground: he refused to talk or to direct his word older word; He said, "I have no satisfaction to give you"; For Avó, he charged him why he had given the right to read a letter that was not for her. He heard without crying the harsh charges of the aunts, which he blackmailed her to ingratitude for her grandmother's dedication to her and her brothers. He firmly, until the departure of the three; At no time did he apologize and only allowed himself, locked in the room, crying for the situation. The next day, when it arrives from school, the grandmother was no longer. A change truck had virtually all the furniture in the house. It was a thud, but with the taste deliberdade. Just over a year later Sandra and her grandmother reconciled each other. It was established and, over time, deepened a very large reciprocal admiration. Never talked about this episode, it was not necessary. It was the marcodo emergence of a woman. Dona Jupira, who also broke many obstacles had surpassed many challenges in her life, did not hide that she admired much, the coherence and firmness of the granddaughter

** In the early 70's Sandra shares the feeling of revolt echoing to the military regime **In the framework of political persecution imposed by the military regime, without direction to revolutionary practice, the needy young people of the correct conception of the world based on Marxism, expressed their non-compliance with the values of life of Brazilian semi-demolonial-bourgeois Brazilian society, fundamentally from the point of the point of view of behavior from the viewing point. Undoubtedly, Sandra wanted to leave the house, looking for new ways. Em1973 interrupts the studies. Who does not work, studies, was the rule in the house.(Faculty), where it is 1974 when moving to the city of Rio de Janeiro.

Since the target of his youth he has contested all this old order of the way he has her understanding, still only sensitive. He was soon able to reflect on the basis of reason on human life, even more so, of the exploited and oppressed masses within the then in force, the fascist military regime was qualified

** The struggle for the liberation of political prisoners: the awareness **

Political awareness will come to be part of the struggle for liberation depression of the circle of friends. When he moves to Rio, Sandra will be with her friend Aline, a talented mining singer whose husband, revolutionary militant was imprisoned. There he follows the process of arrest and participates in solidarity in the struggle for the liberation of political prisoners. As a result, he returns to BH and takes his friend's young son with him to stay at home. Going and returning frequently between BH and Rio, he always took his father's house to help with the expenses. Which could land on money, because he lived on the sale of handicrafts on the streets and beaches of the River.

** The beginning of revolutionary militancy **** married the fight at ** ** 19 ** ** 77, had 4 children and 4 grandchildren **

Sandra marries in February 1977 with her fellow fighting companion, a proletarian love, based not only on mutual inclination a man and a woman, but on their commitment to the revolution. In the process of March she suffers a fainting at the factory; By changing -refill chamber, an antiepiletic use for a while. Manual and repetitive official also aggravates your arthritis problem. If you internal treatment. Then you need to make constant applying compresses of cloths with wax in your hands, elbows and knees to relieve pain.

The couple's house was always a center for political activities, had someone more living in the house. Even after the birth of their children, they hosted relatives and companions for long periods. Early on the children saved that they had no room, not even bed, fixed at home; the accommodation of thee distributed according to the need at each moment. Sandra Semprese would be proud to have offered this education to her children.

By health limitations does not return to factory work. It focuses on neighborhood notralies. Accompanies the youth group, starts adult literacy class with residents of the Lindeia neighborhood, where it marair. Participates in the organization of demonstrations in the City Hall against the abusive collection of prints; For better transport, asphalting and sanitation of the Daregião neighborhoods. The struggle for the health post, which starts with the construction of the building, will gain another dynamic when medical students pass by the verification voluntary and free medical care on weekends. Massa of mass was already having a more defined political objective, still very clear about the line, but clearly surpassing the narrow boundaries of economical work, based on mobilizing the masses to fight for their immediate and defense of their rights.



** The ways ** ** zigzaguantes ** ** of a class practice **In early 1979, after the inauguration of General Figueiredo, the MR8 arrests are triggered. A companion of yours, a student of Biological Sciences at UFMG, Épression. Sandra, already with her first daughter, actively participates in the campaign of her arrest and the acts for her release. The companion is loose after 18 days. Sandra engages in a much more active way in the immediate movement of political prisoners, for the end of persecution and poisonism(This flag unified the left at the time, as a democratic achievement for the immediate liberation of all political prisoners and returns to the exiles, including those banned by the fascist militant regime).Em 2011 e 2012, a companheira Sandra viria a dirigir uma campanha pela puniçãoexemplar para os torturadores e assassinos, mandantes e executores, do regimemilitar fascista, contrapondo-se às linhas, tanto do oportunismo nogerenciamento do velho Estado, de "Comissão da verdade, quanto a do sistema depoder representada pelo milicos, de defesa da anistia ampla geral eirrestrita, realizada com acordo entre o regime em colapso e a oposiçãoliberal, contando com vários setores da esquerda reformista.

O ano de 1979, com explosão das greves operárias, principalmente dosmetalúrgicos nas regiões metropolitanas de São Paulo, Belo Horizonte e Rio deJaneiro, e especialmente tormentoso na região de sua militância, a companheiraatuou intensamente no apoio à greve na Fiat em Betim e à vitoriosa greve naMannesmann. A greve da Mannesmann, comandada pelo companheiro Albenzio, oBoné, deslindou posições com outras de caráter meramente economicista, aoimprimir direção política revolucionária, politizando os operários ao levantaralto em suas manifestações as bandeiras políticas de derrubada revolucionáriada "ditadura militar". A companheira tomou parte dos comitês clandestinos queprepararam e deflagraram a greve na construção civil daquele mesmo ano, quesacudiu a reação com a ocupação do centro de Belo Horizonte. A "revolta dospedreiros" como ficou conhecida sofreu duro golpe dos pelegos comandados porLuiz Inácio, que foi chamado às pressas a esta cidade para sabotar a direçãoda greve e pôr fim a ela.

A primeira prisão política da Sandra ocorre em 1979, na Cidade Industrial,quando fazia campanha de solidariedade aos metalúrgicos em greve em São Paulo.A companheira, como todas as vezes em que foi presa, manteve uma posturaaltiva e firme frente aos esbirros do velho Estado.

The Journal Hora do Povo is launched in August 1979. The following year are organized by the newspaper's sales brigades. Excellent agitator, Sandra will stand out. In one of them held at Sete Square she is arrested porolishes of Dops. The headlines against the government were blunt and corresponded to the longing for democratic freedoms that the masses had aroused from the explosion of strike movements. The political evaluation of the MR8 was that the fascist military regime was deeply divided and had entered the Colapso and the police could no longer keep the brigade members, much less kill or disappear them. The orientation for the militants was to make the squares of the cities in the regime's denunciation and their overthrow. The front of the repression was to resist the arrest, calling on the people to prevent it, provoke the isolation and wear of the police repression, opening the squares of expression and manifestation. And this actually occurred until it occurs in the practice of these democratic rights. Thus a generation of agitators was forged, from which Sandra stood out as one of the most combative eloquent. Win the right to denounce in the public square the dosage government was torn by revolutionary brigade members. In 1982, during finance campaign to strengthen the Povo Horas newspaper, Sandra Esu Companion sold their home from Lindeia to donate money to the fight.

In the work of Bairro Sandra, she began to pay special attention to the organization of women's groups. In 1981, already with two children, mobilizes and commands through the capital streets a march for the freezing of the price of milk, challenging PM's shock beam. The proposal of a specific organization of women was gaining body.** Health problems: the weapon of science and ideology of the proletariat **

Sandra has always faced serious health problems. At 14 he had the first symptoms of rheumatoid arthritis he treated until 1977; From 1989 onwards, autoimmune disease evolves to lupus and the main symptom is the syndromede raynaud, a blood circulation deficiency at the ends of the fingers. Ascrises were almost annual and required high doses of drugs to paracontrol them. He had a seizure in 1994 and is on the brink of death, resulting in an attack by the lupus to the brain. Recovering resumes its political activities. In 2002, it has a new seizure and the exams detect a tumor and logoteve that undergoes surgery for their withdrawal. Subsequently in the follow-up tests, a new tumor and aneurysm detects, it situated the most difficult brain region. During the accompaniment exams and discover that the aneurysm had thrombusted and no longer meant a threat. The second tumor located in the meninge compressed his brain eblocked part of brain functioning, impairing some of his staff, reflecting on some intellectual disability, which required no -tumor removal to decompress his brain. Although this surgery, in 2008, was successfully, and the companion being conscious and could communicate well with family members, had new convulsion and during procedure contracted serious infection that caused her death. The companion died 8 days after hospitalized on July 27, 2016.It treated the conflicts and concerns of young people with a remarkable edisponibility sensitivity. It had no taboo or theme that it would have it. Talked about relationships, dating and marriage; clarified about sexuality, pregnancy and children, about abortion, virginity; About behavior, conduct, about the way of dressing. It waged struggles for children, in particular of the girls. In everything he put the class view, a revolutionary vision. He attacked the feudal bourgeois conceptions, prejudices and reactionaryism, as well as the bourgeois individualism expressed in postmodernism, of all characters, in particular by accordance with women. In his speech there was no trace of arrogance. He spoke values and his practice, showed without reserve and proudly his cocations. He gave special attention to the fight against drugs, all, including oalcool, denouncing how they are used for the alienation of youth.

Acting mainly in the industrial region of Belo Horizonte, Contagem Ebetim and solidarity with the peasant movement, the companion was forging her condition of proletarian, communist and consolidating herself in the most stable nucleus of revolutionary militants, with which she remained until the end of her life, transiting The most different and hard ideological-political clashes in the class struggle.

With the end of the fascist military regime, the product of the revolutionary popular struggle, but due to the small-bourgeois and non-proletarian character who was increasingly prevailing in his orientation, giving hegemony to liberal opposition in the front, the ruling classes could, through the agreement with The generals, impose more harmful undertakes that resulted in the simple return of the military to the quartels and their mere passage to the background of the managing of the Oldest, from which they followed the official political life.



The loss of revolutionary perspective and illusion in the old bourgeois democracy, the abandon of revolutionary violence as a revolutionary way of the conquest of the power, the absence of the minimal organized expression of the ideology of proletariat I made the terrain where revisionism and all opportunism took the direction of popular labor movement. The mistake that with the end of the "military dictatorship" had been weakened the dictatorship of the bourgeoisie, it became the eagerness of the illusion of bourgeois democracy and reformism, once again won, even that timely, in the history of class struggle in the country.And although MR8 fought parliamentary cretinism, enjoying participating in subsidiaries using candidacies as popular tribunes of police denunciation to reveal to the masses the character of classes of society and doesty, to reveal imperialist domination, mainly American, and not country, not He could stop entanglement in the electoral process strengthening the right inside and direction. It was abandoning step by step omobilize, politicize and organize the popular masses to take power. Comisto was moving away from what he had given more strength, leaning on nasms and his mobilization, and increasingly became the fantasy conception that the national democratic revolution would come from the "accumulation of forces" through the peaceful massifestations of masses and the voter. in the occupation of "democratic spaces" in the old state. This was to focus on the construction of a policy-made policy as democratic-national for "breaking with dependence to elibrate the nation." First the peasantry was abandoned, soon focused on articulation of the trade unions and partisan summits regarded poremocratic, dragging all his mass work to support this concept.

During this period, companion Sandra and other companions were launched by organization to legislative candidacies focusing on the purpose of agitation and policy of the exploration system maintained by imperialism, especially American, never being elected. In the midst of these deviations, it was added to the organization consolidating, soon came separations by the most present -luggage and luggage to complete reformism. With directist masolidation under the theses of "uniting the nation to break with adhesion" left open field in the workers' movement so that PT's radical Ademagogy, with its "working class against the employer" gaining more and more influence and dragging the whole fight of a parapontane class of parliamentary cretinism until it reached its electoral triumph in 2002.



** Always for a firm proletarian class position **But it was for these complicated ways that the companion Sandra had agreed correctly in the history of the Revolution and grabbed the defense of the USSR of Lenin and Stalin, the rejection of the betrayal of the XXCONGRESSO of the Communist Party of the Soviet Union \- PCUS and Kruschovism and the defense and the defense inflexible of the proletarian direction of the Stalin comrade forming a sosolid Marxist theoretical base. When liquidationism took over the direction of MR8 and the internal struggle sharpened it was one of the first to take a position by the split led by companion Albenzio, the cap.



** On March 6, 1995, at the age of 40, companion Sandra takes part of a split with national-reformism **

On March 6, 1995, along with hundreds of militants, led by Pelocompany Boné, Sandra is an active part of the Anti-Revistaist split with MR8's reformism, an event with which a new popular and revolutionary domoration stage opened in our country. As a consequence of care, new mass organizations are being built, noclassism, independence and combativity; proclaiming the sweeping disease and all manifestations of opportunism.

Companion Sandra Lima has always been for the proletarian class line. Subsigeration was desperately, buried, which was by refinement, to break this reformist crust. The companion launched themselves shoulder shoulder with her companions in the first lines of combat, from where to reach the high understanding of the science and ideology of the proletariat of our time, Maoism as the third, new and superior stage of development of Marxism, launched by the Labareds of the People's War From Perue the gonzalo thought that directs it. He worked without whimpers, confronting with the review of revisionism and opportunism, in defense of the path of the Brazilian revolution, democratic, agrarian and anti-imperialist revolution, uninterrupted to socialism, in the service of the world revolution and in the course of the luminous communism. of the prolonged struggle and revolutionary diolence as a midwife in history.** The struggle for mobilization, politicization and organization of women of the people **

On March 8, 2000 was held in Belo Horizonte at the headquarters of the Road Transport Walls Union, the Foundation of the Popular Movement Foundation - MFP, a meeting that consolidated the conception, ideology, lineage and program for the new revolutionary movement of women with acriation of acriation a special organization for it.

Sandra was a front line in the struggle for the politicization, promotion and elevation of the political practical of the women of the people, from rejection to the infantilism of feminism, small-bourgeois modern feminism and bourgeois idealism. Always by the class line, it sustained the scientific conception of female oppression, which has its crossing in the emergence of private property, the patriarchal monogamous family, and the division of society into antagonistic classes and that the emancipation of the Damulher is the work of the proletarian revolution. The companion Sandra was ** the main theoretical and practical and ** ** ** ** ** ** Founder of the female movement. **

It follows an excerpt from a letter from Sandra addressed to a nearby companion on the meaning of freedom and incites her to assume her condition as her revolutionary woman:** Companion Sandra has always defended the need for a big revolution in our country **

The companion is one of the main women's leaders and also a revolutionary damage to defense of the rights of the people. The companion takes active to the struggle for urban land taking in Vila Corumbiara(Belohorizer, 1996)and Vila Flag Red(Betim, 1999)and the construction construction popular struggle for housing and the worker league. The companion Sandrafoi responsible, over the last decades, for the ideological, political and theoretical formation of successive generations of young revolutionaries. It has contained with the formation of paintings for the creation of a new popular and revolutionary movement.



** Support to the agrarian revolution and MFP nuclei formation in the field **

Companion Sandra has been a supportive and great propagandist and driver of agrarian revolution in our country as part of the New Democracy Revolution to socialism. It formed generations of young people who have become professors of popular schools in the revolutionary areas of the poor decamponees in various regions of the country. It boosted the formation of MFP nuclei in the LCP areas, boosting the revolutionary organization of peasant women, raising the militancy of hundreds deativists in the struggle for land to those who live and works in it and for the destruction of latifundium as part of the new democracy revolution. Participated in fact in the struggle for the construction of popular relief, support organization toativists, militants and family members, particularly the peasant movement, in the health of health. He gave dozens of lectures for peasant women throughout the country, exposing about the MFP political line and instigating as compounds to throw themselves into the fight. It exposed and explained with particular objectivity, simplicity and scientificity on the line of the movement, gaining the minds and hearts of the peasant masses of our country, which have nompany their reference as women and revolutionary leader.



** The campaign for the punishment of the criminals of the fascist military regime **** More than 40 years of revolutionary militancy **

Its militancy of more than 40 years has been made of firmness of characterore, intellectual honesty, class solidarity without borders, clear position against masses, selfless surrender to the cause, of unconcilious implicit combat to the enemies of the people and persist ever. Its child was never an episodic or clauding because of any of the numerous obstacles that intervenes to the practice and life of the revolutionaries, also forged in the contradictions of the intense and nasted debates of the fierce ideological-political struggles and the critical and self-criticism.



** Propagandist of the cause and agitator of the revolution **

Exceptional Ideological-Political Framework of Many Lapidated Skills Nocalor of Class struggle as a propagandist of the cause and agitator of the Revolution. The companion developed, a disciple that was President Mao Tsetung, a great deal of objective, objective and scientific way on the general linepolitical of the Movement, always relating to facts that would allow us to understand what they were saying, always linking the general to the particular and the direction to the masses. Sensitive and always concerned with the problems and life of the masses, he deeply knew his reality, particularly that of the women of the people, being a great agitator about the masses that reach the masses and the need for their mobilization, organization and politicization, the need for the revolution of new democracy Uninterrupted to socialism, in our country and at the service of the World Revolution, firmly believing that the people of the world together by performing successive cultural proletarian revolutions, humanity will emanate the whole world into the light to the brightness.

To his glorious memory we offer this beautiful poem elaborated in his honor for one of the founders of the revolutionary front of the people's Defense Front:





** Your presence **

Your fragile body eludes only the volcano that dwells in the lurking to untie,

The light of your eyes attentive to aiming at the people to rejoice their eyes,

Your simple beauty, stripped of arrangements, simple of almost austere espartan,

Your serene reason of truths became a theme of the disturbing passion to fight,

Your revolutionary stubbornness was the stone refusal to surrender,

Your voice so serious made of causing disorders is the voice of the mob that comes there,

Voice of sowing winds, making riots to the old order, weave sessionYour fist lifted once so that it will never fall,

Your interrupted flight is eagle that rises in our voice,

Your bright presence so luminous in us forever.



But your body was quiet in the stormy time you announced,

The light of your eyes extinguished to be the flash of the new dawn that will come,

Your simplicity left to be an example to everyone,

Your reason was wanted in the cause condemned to triumph,

Your stubbornness has ceased to make unenforceable to persist,

Your voice silent in the corner of hope and certainty,

Your fist in Laughter rested on the fury of the masses,

Your flight posed to challenge the summons,

Your presence was absence to gain battles beyond death,

What do you complain to? Order!

That sickles and hammers are sorry,

That tree to the highest summit the banner,

Who sound trumpets,

That ruffle drums,

That wield rifles,

To you, we answer, gift companion!



** Companion Sandra Lima: Present in the fight!**

** Hono and glory eternal to the heroes and heroines of our people!**

** Awaken the revolutionary fury of the woman!**

