# That women, workers of Ukraine, of Russia do like the women of March 8, 1917 in Russia, against the imperialist war!

Author: fannyhill

Description: In St. Petersburg, on March 8, 1917 the women of the capital guided a great event that claimed the end of the war, so c ...

Time: 2023-03-06T19:24:00+01:00

Images: ['[donne_pietrogrado.jpg](https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiegAwIS7GAnMNpdFfraAdKiNtx3dYCxt9eJHT8eIDrhoAm6aRdpp-TXo3lKnRyaQrhpC2ncGIWz_U1gRE2WqMzKy_Aso-kEiNJkXAyNfQtcX7W9SE8QRSGm36sZYoJip_jmITXLXPcjY9L_uecsac-_T-zgVOUrE4TjRJ2xM-gnaEw3peBVI1PeFNscw/w400-h200/donne_pietrogrado.jpg)']

<!--METADATA-->

In St. Petersburg, on March 8, 1917 the women of the capital guided a greatmanifestation that ** claimed the end of the war, ** so that on March 81917 he remained in history to indicate the beginning of the Russian revolution of February.

[![](Images/femminismo proletario rivoluzionario/2023-03-06T19-24-00-01-00/donne_pietrogrado.jpg)](https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiegAwIS7GAnMNpdFfraAdKiNtx3dYCxt9eJHT8eIDrhoAm6aRdpp-TXo3lKnRyaQrhpC2ncGIWz_U1gRE2WqMzKy_Aso-kEiNJkXAyNfQtcX7W9SE8QRSGm36sZYoJip_jmITXLXPcjY9L_uecsac-_T-zgVOUrE4TjRJ2xM-gnaEw3peBVI1PeFNscw/s400/donne_pietrogrado.jpg)On the International Women's Day in 1917, the textile workers in the Vyborg of Pietograd pitched off on strike, abandoned Gistilabilizioni and, hundreds of them, were made from the factory by calling workers to the strike and hiring violent clashes with the police and army.

The women launched sticks, stones and snowballs against the hesitant windows and worsened in the workplace, ** asking for the war of the war and the return of their men from the front. **

The soldiers guarding the tram deposits were convinced by women from the tramway company to join them and the carriages were reversed to be used as barricades against the police.

